snippet.textDisplay:
I am partial to Arnob, I always have been. That makes me partial to Coke studio. But nearly 10M views within a week is absolutely amazing. Well done Pritam! I’m sure your father is very very proud of you right now. You are keeping his legacy alive and taking it to new heights.

It’s worth mentioning that Pritam’s last creation Deora is the most successful Coke Studio Bangla track so far, and from the look of it, he is 2 for 2 on this!

This particular song has so many layers, just like every other song. You have to listen to it over and over again concentrating on different aspects of it at each time. After listening to it over may be a hundred times, I finally read the lyrics, pausing after every sentence and taking in the philosophy behind. And I am in tears. I don’t know how to express the pride, the gratitude, the sense of completeness, wholesomeness I feel listening to Coke Studio Bangla. Keep it up guys!
